Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.41,0:01:46.63,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1015,514)\2c&H7E9CCF&\c&H356BCF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H0C0C0C&}新的魔法使出現
